# Fluff Date: 2026-03-18 15:07:44
<overview>
<p>Stealth sniper squads combine airborne insertion capability, sneak suit concealment, and precision marksman training in a compact special operations element. Armed with sniper rifles and magnum auto-pistols for close defense, these squads deploy covertly behind enemy lines to eliminate high-value targets from concealed positions, relying on stealth technology to avoid detection before and after engagement.</p>
</overview>

